    "name": "Second Stellar",
    "steam_appid": 3176850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/72c95cec292eb2cf6df89866fe06145f.poster.avif?t=1765690004\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/72c95cec292eb2cf6df89866fe06145f.webm?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/72c95cec292eb2cf6df89866fe06145f.mp4?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《穹海双星》是一款以角色构筑为核心的类幸存者Roguelike游戏。你将同时操纵两名角色，突破敌人重围，挑战强力BOSS。游戏提供了丰富的武器选择，你可以自由搭配，在实战中尝试可能的组合，探寻星海之中的诸多奥秘。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/3c64f839c229bfd9b345d222b72b21d2.webp?t=1765690004\" width=596 height=13 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/25790a3254e2f027dcd917119aeb60b7.poster.avif?t=1765690004\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/25790a3254e2f027dcd917119aeb60b7.webm?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/25790a3254e2f027dcd917119aeb60b7.mp4?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战术成双 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于星海之中需要强大的火力支撑；星海旅者们能在战斗中读取其它世界的记忆，使用那些独特能力，来使战斗占据上风。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他类幸存者游戏不同，每把武器都具有多种主动技能和被动技能，需要熟练运用才能充分发挥武器潜力。战斗中，你可以随时切换角色，使用不同武器协同作战，进而产生质的变化——无限的角色组合与武器、物品搭配正等待你发现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/3c64f839c229bfd9b345d222b72b21d2.webp?t=1765690004\" width=596 height=13 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/4de42a847cc1739862346a03ca259d27.poster.avif?t=1765690004\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/4de42a847cc1739862346a03ca259d27.webm?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/4de42a847cc1739862346a03ca259d27.mp4?t=1765690004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻回遗失的传说 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在寰宇之旅中，你将穿行于各片战场，对抗来自遥远追忆的强大精英，直面它们多样的攻势。发挥旅途中获得的力量，击败它们，赢得你的战利品。解锁多样的角色专属技能，不断拓展独特的流派构筑，在冒险中更进一步。.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176850/extras/3c64f839c229bfd9b345d222b72b21d2.webp?t=1765690004\" width=596 height=13 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >行至星海苍穹 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追随双子星海旅者爱丝福德妮与埃里达妮的步伐，踏上冒险之旅，探索未知，寻找真相——穹海双星的故事正在上演！作为神秘追忆之力的掌控者，她们的旅途将奇遇不断——既有纷争，亦有合作。你将结识盟友，遭遇敌人，邂逅各种立场的人们——也许还能与他们结成同盟。为了探明“远航者”背后的真相，你必须尽可能多的寻求帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
